---

---

<section
	class="bg-mist relative flex min-h-[calc(100svh-var(--nav-height))] flex-col overflow-hidden pt-(--nav-height)"
	aria-labelledby="hero-heading"
>
	<div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0" aria-hidden="true">
		<svg
			class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full"
			viewBox="0 0 1440 800"
			fill="none"
			xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
			preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice"
			aria-hidden="true"
		>
			<path
				d="M-50 600 Q200 500 400 520 T800 480 T1200 450 T1490 420"
				stroke="var(--color-navy)"
				stroke-width="1"
				opacity="0.05"></path>
			<path
				d="M-50 560 Q160 460 360 480 T760 440 T1160 410 T1490 380"
				stroke="var(--color-navy)"
				stroke-width="0.5"
				opacity="0.04"></path>
			<path
				d="M-50 300 Q200 350 450 320 T900 280 T1350 250 T1490 240"
				stroke="var(--color-navy)"
				stroke-width="1"
				opacity="0.05"></path>
			<line
				x1="800"
				y1="100"
				x2="800"
				y2="700"
				stroke="var(--color-navy)"
				stroke-width="0.5"
				opacity="0.03"
				stroke-dasharray="4 8"></line>
		</svg>
	</div>

	<div
		class="relative z-10 mx-auto grid w-full max-w-7xl flex-1 grid-cols-1 items-start gap-12 px-6 py-12 sm:px-8 sm:py-16 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.1fr)_minmax(320px,420px)] lg:items-center lg:gap-16"
	>
		<div class="hero-reveal flex max-w-3xl flex-col gap-8 lg:gap-10">
			<p class="font-body text-navy/68 text-sm font-semibold tracking-[0.16em] uppercase">
				Logistik digital untuk tim pemilik bisnis, operasional, keuangan, dan layanan pelanggan
			</p>
			<h1
				id="hero-heading"
				class="font-display text-navy max-w-[10ch] leading-[1.02] font-black tracking-tight"
				style="font-size: clamp(2.85rem, 7vw, 5.4rem);"
			>
				Pengiriman bisnis,<br />
				lebih jelas dari<br />
				awal sampai tiba.
			</h1>

			<p class="font-body text-charcoal-mid max-w-[62ch] text-base leading-8 sm:text-[1.0625rem]">
				LintasNusa membantu tim Anda merapikan pickup, pelacakan, SLA, retur, dan klaim dalam satu
				alur kerja yang terukur. Kami memulai dari pemetaan kebutuhan operasional, lalu menyusun
				alur yang paling masuk akal untuk lane, bukti serah-terima, dan tindak lanjut saat ada
				kendala.
			</p>

			<div class="border-navy/10 grid gap-4 border-t pt-6 sm:grid-cols-3 sm:gap-6">
				<div class="grid gap-1.5">
					<p class="font-body text-navy text-sm font-semibold">Pemetaan lane dan pickup</p>
					<p class="font-body text-charcoal-mid text-sm leading-6">
						Kami mulai dari volume, wilayah prioritas, dan pola penjemputan tim Anda.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="grid gap-1.5">
					<p class="font-body text-navy text-sm font-semibold">Aturan respons saat ada kendala</p>
					<p class="font-body text-charcoal-mid text-sm leading-6">
						SLA, eskalasi, dan alur retur disusun supaya tim tidak bekerja dengan asumsi.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="grid gap-1.5">
					<p class="font-body text-navy text-sm font-semibold">Bukti operasional yang dibutuhkan</p>
					<p class="font-body text-charcoal-mid text-sm leading-6">
						Scan, foto POD, dan histori klaim dipilih sesuai kebutuhan audit dan layanan pelanggan.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:flex-wrap sm:items-center">
				<a
					href="#layanan"
					class="cta-primary bg-orange font-body focus:outline-teal hover:bg-orange-hover block min-h-11 rounded-md px-6 py-4 text-center text-[15px] font-semibold text-white no-underline transition-all duration-150 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-[0_10px_24px_rgba(169,60,25,0.18)] focus:outline-2 focus:outline-offset-3 active:translate-y-0 active:scale-[.99] active:shadow-none sm:min-w-[17rem]"
				>
					Bahas alur pengiriman dengan tim kami
				</a>
				<a
					href="#platform"
					class="cta-secondary group text-teal font-body hover:text-navy focus:outline-teal inline-flex min-h-11 items-center gap-2 py-2 text-sm font-semibold no-underline transition-colors duration-150 focus:rounded-sm focus:outline-2 focus:outline-offset-4"
				>
					Tinjau pendekatan operasional kami
					<svg
						width="14"
						height="14"
						viewBox="0 0 14 14"
						fill="none"
						aria-hidden="true"
						class="transition-transform duration-150 group-hover:translate-x-0.5"
					>
						<path
							d="M2 7H12M12 7L7.5 2.5M12 7L7.5 11.5"
							stroke="currentColor"
							stroke-width="1.5"
							stroke-linecap="round"
							stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
					</svg>
				</a>
			</div>

			<p class="font-body text-charcoal-mid max-w-[48ch] text-sm leading-6">
				Pendekatan kami tetap konsultatif: sesi awal dipakai untuk membaca kebutuhan lane, risiko
				operasional, dan standar bukti yang harus dijaga sebelum implementasi dibahas lebih jauh.
			</p>
		</div>

		<aside
			class="hero-reveal border-navy/12 relative w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[1.5rem] border bg-white p-6 shadow-[0_18px_42px_rgba(15,39,66,0.07)] sm:p-8"
			aria-label="Pendekatan konsultasi operasional LintasNusa"
		>
			<div class="bg-mist absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-20"></div>
			<div
				class="border-navy/10 relative inline-flex items-center rounded-full border bg-white px-3 py-1"
			>
				<span class="font-body text-navy text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.14em] uppercase">
					Sesi awal yang kami jalankan
				</span>
			</div>
			<p
				class="font-display text-navy relative mt-5 max-w-[17ch] text-[clamp(1.7rem,3.6vw,2.4rem)] leading-[1.08] font-bold tracking-tight"
			>
				Kami merapikan alur kirim lebih dulu, baru membicarakan sistem yang paling pas.
			</p>
			<p class="font-body text-charcoal-mid relative mt-4 max-w-[34ch] text-sm leading-7">
				Pembahasan awal difokuskan pada titik rawan operasional, siapa yang perlu melihat apa, dan
				bukti lapangan apa yang harus selalu tersedia saat ada pertanyaan dari pelanggan.
			</p>

			<ol class="relative mt-8 grid gap-4">
				<li class="border-navy/10 grid grid-cols-[auto_1fr] gap-4 border-b pb-4">
					<span
						class="bg-navy text-mist font-display inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-full text-sm font-bold"
						>01</span
					>
					<div class="grid gap-1">
						<p class="font-body text-navy text-sm font-semibold">
							Membaca lane, pickup, dan beban tim
						</p>
						<p class="font-body text-charcoal-mid text-sm leading-6">
							Kami identifikasi wilayah prioritas, ritme pickup, dan titik serah yang paling sering
							menimbulkan antrean atau keterlambatan.
						</p>
					</div>
				</li>
				<li class="border-navy/10 grid grid-cols-[auto_1fr] gap-4 border-b pb-4">
					<span
						class="bg-navy text-mist font-display inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-full text-sm font-bold"
						>02</span
					>
					<div class="grid gap-1">
						<p class="font-body text-navy text-sm font-semibold">
							Menentukan siapa yang butuh visibilitas dan kapan harus bergerak
						</p>
						<p class="font-body text-charcoal-mid text-sm leading-6">
							Pemilik bisnis, operasional, keuangan, dan layanan pelanggan hanya melihat informasi
							yang relevan untuk keputusan mereka.
						</p>
					</div>
				</li>
				<li class="grid grid-cols-[auto_1fr] gap-4">
					<span
						class="bg-orange text-mist font-display inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-full text-sm font-bold"
						>03</span
					>
					<div class="grid gap-1">
						<p class="font-body text-navy text-sm font-semibold">
							Menyepakati bukti serah-terima, retur, dan alur klaim
						</p>
						<p class="font-body text-charcoal-mid text-sm leading-6">
							Scan, foto POD, histori retur, dan target tanggapan disusun supaya kendala tidak
							berputar lama di customer service.
						</p>
					</div>
				</li>
			</ol>

			<dl
				class="border-navy/10 mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 border-t pt-6 sm:grid-cols-3 sm:gap-x-5"
			>
				<div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
					<dt class="font-body text-charcoal-mid text-xs leading-5">Kepatuhan scan</dt>
					<dd class="font-display text-navy text-[1.45rem] leading-none font-bold tracking-tight">
						97,9%
					</dd>
					<dd class="font-body text-charcoal-mid text-xs leading-5">Data 2025</dd>
				</div>
				<div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
					<dt class="font-body text-charcoal-mid text-xs leading-5">Klaim standar selesai</dt>
					<dd class="font-display text-navy text-[1.45rem] leading-none font-bold tracking-tight">
						91%
					</dd>
					<dd class="font-body text-charcoal-mid text-xs leading-5">Dalam 2 x 24 jam</dd>
				</div>
				<div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
					<dt class="font-body text-charcoal-mid text-xs leading-5">Wilayah jangkauan</dt>
					<dd class="font-display text-navy text-[1.45rem] leading-none font-bold tracking-tight">
						247
					</dd>
					<dd class="font-body text-charcoal-mid text-xs leading-5">Kota dan kabupaten</dd>
				</div>
			</dl>
		</aside>
	</div>
</section>
